data.description: Welcome to this 2 bed, 1 bath home located in the heart of Bakersfield, set on a spacious 6969 sq ft lot. Ideal for first-time buyers or those looking to downsize, this cozy residence offers a comfortable and inviting living space. The kitchen features ample counter space, making meal preps a breeze, while the adjacent living room provides a perfect gathering spot for families and friends to enjoy quality time together. Additionally, with its prime location and potential for rental income, this home could also be a lucrative investment property for savvy investors. Don't miss the opportunity to make this versatile property your own.
